1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,520
Cada dia,
cientos de cosas

2
00:00:01,520 --> 00:00:03,680
utiles acaban
donde no deberian.

3
00:00:03,680 --> 00:00:04,600
Cientos.

4
00:00:04,600 --> 00:00:06,480
Se pierden muebles,
electrodomesticos,

5
00:00:06,480 --> 00:00:07,880
objetos que funcionan...

6
00:00:07,880 --> 00:00:09,440
porque falta
una conexion.

7
00:00:09,440 --> 00:00:11,080
Alguien lo deja,
alguien lo necesita,

8
00:00:11,080 --> 00:00:12,520
pero no
se encuentran.

9
00:00:12,520 --> 00:00:13,840
Va, que os
lo cuento.

10
00:00:13,840 --> 00:00:15,080
Renovar,
reutilizar,

11
00:00:15,080 --> 00:00:16,040
compartir.

12
00:00:16,040 --> 00:00:17,440
Es mas facil
que tirarlo.

13
00:00:17,440 --> 00:00:18,720
Y alguien cerca
lo aprovecharia

14
00:00:18,720 --> 00:00:19,720
encantado.

15
00:00:19,720 --> 00:00:21,040
Antes de tirar,
pensad

16
00:00:21,040 --> 00:00:23,160
si alguien mas
lo puede querer.

17
00:00:23,160 --> 00:00:24,680
Nos vemos
en el proximo paseo.

